Package: rayrender
Type: Package
Title: Raytrace Spheres
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2019-03-11
Author: Tyler Morgan-Wall
Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: A raytracer for spheres, planes, and cubes. Uses a tidy `tibble` input to build scenes. Based off of Peter Shirley's "Ray Tracing in One Weekend" and "Ray Tracing: The Next Week".
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    RcppParallel,
    rayshader,
    assertthat,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    png
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppParallel
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
SystemRequirements: GNU make
